    <h1 class="section-heading">🚀 Job Post: Trainee Developer</h1>
    <p class="section-content">
    <p class="section-content">
      We’re looking for passionate, curious folks to work with.
    </p>
    <p class="section-content">
      This is a full time role, and will be a good fit for you if you’re looking to kick-start your software dev career.
      You are expected to be familiar with at least one programming language, and to demonstrate a strong ability to
      learn. We also welcome your application if your educational background or work experience are in a different
      domain and you’re looking to transition into a dev career.
    </p>
    <p class="section-content">
      The lack of diversity in technology is a problem. To do our part in addressing this, we are
      <strong>keen on hearing from women and other under-represented communities</strong> in India for this position.
    </p>
    <p class="section-content action-item">
      👉 Please submit this form to apply:
      <a target="_blank" href="https://forms.gle/k2vetfGMGJtpFm8ZA">https://forms.gle/k2vetfGMGJtpFm8ZA</a>.
    </p>
